# Helm Template Files - YAML Linter Ignore
#
# These files contain Helm template syntax (Go templates) that YAML linters
# cannot parse. This is expected behavior - Helm templates are not valid YAML
# until processed by Helm.
#
# The files in templates/ directory are valid Helm templates and will work
# correctly when deployed with Helm.
#
# To validate these files, use:
#   helm lint ./helm-charts/sample-app
#   helm template ./helm-charts/sample-app | kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f -

